OL,3,CStarmer says state of prisons is
OL,4,C'worse' than he thought
OL,6,FThe prime minister says the state of
OL,7,Fprisons is "worse than I thought" as
OL,8,Fthe government attempts to deal with
OL,9,Fthe overcrowding crisis.
OL,11,F"I'm pretty shocked that it's been
OL,12,Fallowed to get into that situation",
OL,13,FStarmer told journalists on a flight
OL,14,Fto Washington DC for the Nato summit.
