OL,3,CStarmer says state of prisons is
OL,4,C'worse' than he thought
OL,6,FThe PM was asked if he was surprised
OL,7,Fby the state of the public finances,
OL,8,Fto which he replied: "Some of what
OL,9,Fwe've found is shocking, not so much
OL,10,Fabout the finances, but I have to say
OL,11,Fon prisons. The situation is worse
OL,12,Fthan I thought it was."
OL,14,FHe accused the government of being
OL,15,F"reckless" with Britain's jails and
OL,16,Fpromised the government will be
OL,17,F"saying more" about prisons in "short
OL,18,Forder".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
