OL,3,CStarmer says state of prisons is
OL,4,C'worse' than he thought
OL,6,FReports have been swirling about the
OL,7,Faction Labour will take to tackle the
OL,8,Fcrisis in jails - ITV News understands
OL,9,Fby the end of this week the government
OL,10,Fis likely to decide it will release
OL,11,Fmore prisoners early.
OL,13,FThe prison population is currently at
OL,14,F87,453, edging dangerously close to
OL,15,Fthe maximum capacity of 88,864.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
