OL,3,CStarmer says state of prisons is
OL,4,C'worse' than he thought
OL,6,FThe Ministry of Justice projects the
OL,7,Fpopulation will rise further to hit
OL,8,F99,300 by the end of 2025. While new
OL,9,Fprisons are being built, they can't
OL,10,Fkeep up with the demand for cells,
OL,11,Fwith only 4,400 new places planned
OL,12,Fcompared to 12,000 more prisoners.
OL,14,FIt's likely the new Justice Secretary
OL,15,FShabana Mahmood will reduce the point
OL,16,Fat which prisoners with fixed end
OL,17,Fdates to their sentences can be
OL,18,Freleased to tackle the crisis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
