OL,3,CStarmer says state of prisons is
OL,4,C'worse' than he thought
OL,6,FEven the controversial decision to
OL,7,Flower the automatic release point
OL,8,Fwould only delay the prison
OL,9,Fovercrowding crisis by 18 months.
OL,11,FMinistry of Justice (MoJ) sources
OL,12,Fstress the release is on licence and
OL,13,Fthat people can be returned to jail if
OL,14,Fthey break the conditions of their
OL,15,Frelease.
OL,17,FITV News understands Conservative
OL,18,FJustice Secretary Alex Chalk was
OL,19,Fconsidering the same change with
OL,20,Fexclusions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
