OL,3,CStarmer says state of prisons is
OL,4,C'worse' than he thought
OL,6,FThe previous government under Rishi
OL,7,FSunak triggered emergency measures to
OL,8,Ftackle the crisis, including allowing
OL,9,Fsome prisoners to be released up to 70
OL,10,Fdays early.
OL,12,FThe End of Custody Supervised License
OL,13,FScheme (ECSL) initially involved
OL,14,Finmates being released up to 18 days
OL,15,Fearly. That was then extended to
OL,16,Fbetween 35 and 60 days in March, and
OL,17,Ffurther extended to 70 days in May.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
