OL,3,CStarmer says state of prisons is
OL,4,C'worse' than he thought
OL,6,FSources tell ITV News the plans to
OL,7,Flower the automatic release point
OL,8,Fneeded to go alongside an overhaul in
OL,9,Fsentencing that would see fewer people
OL,10,Fsent to jail for short sentences.
OL,12,FAfter his election victory last week,
OL,13,FSir Keir Starmer appointed James
OL,14,FTimpson OBE, of Timpson shoe repairs,
OL,15,Fas prison's minister.
OL,17,FTimpson, who is now a Lord, has
OL,18,Fadvocated for employing former
OL,19,Fprisoners and reforming the UK's
OL,20,Fprison system.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
